<X3D profile="Immersive" version="4.0">
<head>
  <meta name="title" content="Pleistocene Hall (Samwel)"/>
  <meta name="description" content="Pleistocene Hall is a named space in Furlongs plan (Feranec et al. 2007 Fig. 2). The cave is the Cave of the Magic Pools with several standing water pools (Wintu medicine men bathed for magic strength)."/>
  <meta name="rights" content="Interpretive: Room size and ellipsoidal shape, every speleothem, breakdown blocks, the exact pool placement, lighting, and surface texture. LAYOUT: global_position/level_order/stream_bbox are interpretive staging f"/>
</head>
